  "hash_before": "2e415e0eca460e145f70201b0e6fef213994d455812104e0f2bb761cb2f13267",
  "heading_path": "热力学第一定律",
  "intensity": "STRUCTURAL",
  "line_count": 103,
  "masked_text": "[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02893:bd1dacf9c670]]\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02894:e2a3bbd82c45]]\n绝热自由膨胀的初态和末态都可以用状态方程描述，但中间过程不是准静态过程，因此[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02895:558149d9777b]]{不能}套用 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02896:d28eedc9cfb0]]。这正是课件反复强调的[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02897:a8aca1eb62fa]]。\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02898:c7cf8781b913]]\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02899:5a100a24f5ee]]\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02900:ff2eb9e78880]]{solution}\n在 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02901:2e67e1c0bb16]] 过程中\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02902:1178df907c55]]对 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02903:0231d1cfd597]] 过程：[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02904:cc2f33f4a634]]\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02905:06b3847e1b6f]]{solution}\n\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02906:2528b37533fd]]\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02907:ff2eb9e78880]]{solution}\n [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02908:44f736b43821]]\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02909:06b3847e1b6f]]{solution}\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02910:d734f763580c]]\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02911:ff2eb9e78880]]{solution}\n多方过程仍是准静态体积功，先把 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02912:624cbe11d8e1]] 用 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02913:ccbeb0af5c25]] 表示，再沿体积积分：\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02914:d844480302fe]]\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02915:06b3847e1b6f]]{solution}\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02916:6e845856c1f5]]\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02917:ff2eb9e78880]]{solution}\n三条路径的始末态相同，所以 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02918:f136a0ac9f16]] 相同；但作功由 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02919:624cbe11d8e1]]-[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02920:ccbeb0af5c25]] 图下方面积决定。[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02921:0e9b9cf6d26b]] 是压缩过程，[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02922:04ea313d1ba7]]，所以两条任意路径中气体对外作功都为负。[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02923:1adf85bea90c]] 在绝热线下方，压缩时面积较小，外界作功没有绝热线那么多，即[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02924:5a27e150ed24]]更小，所以由[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02925:1cde93150cd7]]不变得知[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02926:7473d2a2de0e]]，气体要从外界吸热。 在绝热线上方，压缩时面积较大，外界作功比绝热线多，所以[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02927:5a27e150ed24]]更大，由[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02928:1cde93150cd7]]不变得知[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02929:7473d2a2de0e]]，气体要对外界放热。\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02930:06b3847e1b6f]]{solution}\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02931:d15074c66317]]\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02932:ff2eb9e78880]]{solution}\n理想气体沿曲线 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02933:12124737fb7f]] 过程吸热 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02934:daddd264c7fa]]。但是温度不变所以内能不变，必然对外做功[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02935:daddd264c7fa]]，再沿 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02936:73d79fd50afb]] 回到初态，此过程初末温度不变，且外界做功[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02937:d3a7f4ad3553]]，所以放热[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02938:d3a7f4ad3553]]，所以整个过程吸热 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02939:2d6631fad941]]。\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02940:06b3847e1b6f]]{solution}\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02941:b00d127d758f]]\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02942:ff2eb9e78880]]{solution}\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02943:41f51b159a13]]\n再[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02944:4f2a8508bbb8]]，进而 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02945:b24714b918aa]]。于是 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02946:d6c1a054e721]]。\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02947:06b3847e1b6f]]{solution}\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02948:726c48b577c5]]\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02949:ff2eb9e78880]]{solution}\n由[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02950:df91b9d8bde2]]到[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02951:ccd2b4a0ba37]]内能增加[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02952:510a2efb6f84]]，[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02953:c4ca909f3e64]]温度相同，所以内能相同。从[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02954:df91b9d8bde2]]到[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02955:2a6f81ee6375]]吸热[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02956:3b39c5b4f5f4]]，所以必定对外做功[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02957:514264ce37e9]] \n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02958:06b3847e1b6f]]{solution}\n",
  "mode": "REWRITE",
